          <head>
            <note type="contents-note">This manuscript contains: The Psalms, according to the Peshitta version, Ps. cli. being added at the end.; The Canticles. In total, including sub-sections, this manuscript contains 11 items.</note>
            <listRelation type="Wright-BL-Taxonomy">
