            <msItem xml:id="a1" n="1" defective="true">
              <locus from="10a"/>
              <title xml:lang="en">The Psalms, according to the Peshitta version, Ps.
                        cli. being added at the end.</title>
              <rubric xml:lang="syr">ܡܙܡܘܪܐ ܕܝܠܢܝܐ ܕܝܠ̣ܗ ܕܕܘܝܕ</rubric>
              <note>The <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܡܪ̈ܡܝܬܐ</foreign> and <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܫܘ̈ܒܚܐ</foreign> are marked
                        on the margins; and there is a farther division in the text into Services 
                        (<foreign xml:lang="syr">ܬܫܡ̈ܫܬܐ</foreign>) according to the usual canonical hours, commencing, in the present
                        state of the manuscript.</note>
              <note>The missing portions are: <bibl>Ps. i. 1—xxix. 3; xxxi. 22—xxxvii. 25;
                           xxxix. 3—lxxxviii. 8; and xciii. 3—xcv. 11</bibl>. </note>
              <msItem xml:id="b1" n="2" defective="true">
